Build a simple assistant that listens to your voice and
performs actions like:

*Searching Wikipedia
*Opening Websites
*Telling the time
*Speaking back a greeting

Features:
    *Voice Input(using microphone)
    *Text-to-speech responses
    *Perform basics tasks(open google,search wikipedia,tell)

Requirements:
    *pip install pyaudio
    *pip install speechrecognition pyttsx3 wikipedia